    "summary": "The user, acting as a high school teacher, prompts the assistant to draft lesson content on substantive due process. The conversation evolves from a general explanation to a specific request for how to address critics of the doctrine. The assistant responds by dismissing the critics' arguments and endorsing the judicial approach as the \"better way.\"",
